nodes.text: The Oevvaor Jet Catamaran, also referred to as the Wookiee catamaran, or Oevvaor cataraman was a well-known Wookiee vehicle manufactured by Appazanna Engineering Works. They were named after the oevvaor, a sea creature native to Kashyyyk. During the Battle of Kashyyyk, the catamarans were used to assist the Republic in defending Kachirho.
